{
  "stem": "3040.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At first, I was working under the supervision of a young German who was an electrician.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was working with him maybe for three months.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I learned a lot from him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I really became an electrician under his supervision.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then he was called into the army, and I was the only one in charge of everything.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So he gave me the keys, because there was a, you know, a storage room where they had the circuit breakers, wiring, bulb-- light bulbs, and other things which are necessary to-- for-- to maintain it.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was all of a sudden in charge of everything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when the [GERMAN], the soldier who was in charge of our-- of our transport, he wanted a light bulb, he had to come to me and give me bread for it.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I sold him-- the German-- light bulbs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This is the situation.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Of course, you cannot compare.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "This was not a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was a work camp, and the conditions were very lenient.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And there was not much supervision from the SS.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was just the Organisation Todt who had things to say.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was for their benefit that we worked for-- for them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only Jewish men.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No other nationalities there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not from there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why-- why escape from that kind of--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Much better.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there are people here who survived that camp who I am in touch with.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We sometimes reminisce about the times there in Wüstegiersdorf.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Made friends there, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in fact, after-- this lasted for nine months-- and it was exactly February 16, 1945.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were evacuated from Wüstegiersdorf and march westward into Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The destination then was Flossenburg.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
